ciscoSwitchNetflowMIB.name: ciscoSwitchNetflowMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

ciscoSwitchNetflowMIB.contactinfo: Cisco Systems Customer Service Postal: 170 W Tasman Drive San Jose, CA 95134 USA Tel: +1 800 553-NETS E-mail: cs-lan-switch-snmp@cisco.com
ciscoSwitchNetflowMIB.description: This MIB module defines management objects for the Netflow features on Cisco Layer 2 and Layer 3 devices.

CsnNetflowDirectionTypes.name: CsnNetflowDirectionTypes
CsnNetflowDirectionTypes.description: Defines the various Netflow direction types. 'none' - no Netflow direction is supported. 'ingress' - Netflow direction is ingress. 'egress' - Netflow direction is egress. 'ingressAndEgress' - Netflow direction is both ingress and egress.

csnNetflowDirectionType.name: csnNetflowDirectionType
csnNetflowDirectionType.description: This object specifies the direction type of Netflow enabled on this system.

csnUsageThreshExceedNotifEnable.name: csnUsageThreshExceedNotifEnable
csnUsageThreshExceedNotifEnable.description: This object specifies whether the system produces the csnUsageThreshExceededNotif. A 'false' value will prevent csnUsageThreshExceededNotif notifications from being generated by this system.

csnUsageThreshTable.name: csnUsageThreshTable
csnUsageThreshTable.description: A table containing Netflow table usage monitoring configuration information.

csnUsageThreshEntry.name: csnUsageThreshEntry
csnUsageThreshEntry.description: A conceptual row of csnUsageThreshTable, containing the Netflow table usage monitoring configuration information.

csnUsageDirection.name: csnUsageDirection
csnUsageDirection.description: This object specifies the direction of Netflow on the system.

csnUsageThreshold.name: csnUsageThreshold
csnUsageThreshold.description: This object specifies the Netflow table usage threshold in percentage value. When the value of this object is set to zero, Netflow table usage monitoring is disabled. When the value of this object is set to greater than zero, Netflow table usage monitoring is enabled.

csnUsageInterval.name: csnUsageInterval
csnUsageInterval.description: This object specifies the interval in seconds over which the Netflow table usage (the value of csnUtilization) will be compared against the threshold specified by csnUsageThreshold.

csnUtilizationTable.name: csnUtilizationTable
csnUtilizationTable.description: A table containing Netflow table utilization information of each switching engine and a Newflow direction type.

csnUtilizationEntry.name: csnUtilizationEntry
csnUtilizationEntry.description: A conceptual row of csnUtilizationTable, containing the Netflow table utilization information for a particular switching engine and a particular Netflow type.

csnUtilization.name: csnUtilization
csnUtilization.description: This object indicates the percentage of Netflow table utilization.

csnNetflowTableSizeTable.name: csnNetflowTableSizeTable
csnNetflowTableSizeTable.description: A table containing Netflow table size information of each Netflow type supported in the system.

csnNetflowTableSizeEntry.name: csnNetflowTableSizeEntry
csnNetflowTableSizeEntry.description: A conceptual row of csnNetflowTableSizeTable, containing the Netflow table size information for a particular Netflow type.

csnNetflowTableTotalEntries.name: csnNetflowTableTotalEntries
csnNetflowTableTotalEntries.description: This object indicates the total number of entries in the Netflow table for a particular Netflow direction type.

csnSamplerTotal.name: csnSamplerTotal
csnSamplerTotal.description: This object indicates the total number of Netflow samplers in the device.

csnSamplerAvailable.name: csnSamplerAvailable
csnSamplerAvailable.description: This object indicates the number of Netflow samplers available in the system.

csnUsageThreshExceededNotif.name: csnUsageThreshExceededNotif
csnUsageThreshExceededNotif.description: A csnUsageThreshExceededNotif is sent if the Netflow table usage has exceeded the configured threshold specified by csnUsageThreshold.

csnGlobalGroup.name: csnGlobalGroup
csnGlobalGroup.description: A collection of objects providing global Netflow type configuration.

csnUsageThreshNotifControlGroup.name: csnUsageThreshNotifControlGroup
csnUsageThreshNotifControlGroup.description: A collection of objects providing enabling/disabling of the Netflow table usage threshold notifications.

csnUsageThreshGroup.name: csnUsageThreshGroup
csnUsageThreshGroup.description: A collection of objects providing Netflow table usage threshold information and configuration.

csnUtilizationGroup.name: csnUtilizationGroup
csnUtilizationGroup.description: A collection of objects providing Netflow utilization information.

csnUsageThreshNotifGroup.name: csnUsageThreshNotifGroup
csnUsageThreshNotifGroup.description: A collection of notifications providing Netflow table usage threshold exceeded notification.

csnNetflowTableSizeGroup.name: csnNetflowTableSizeGroup
csnNetflowTableSizeGroup.description: A collection of objects providing Netflow table size information.

csnSamplerGroup.name: csnSamplerGroup
csnSamplerGroup.description: A collection of objects providing Netflow sampler information.
